{"id":139171,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/简讯：中国直升机逼近日本护卫舰/","date":"2011-03-08T20:10:30Z","modified":"2011-03-08T20:10:30Z","title":"简讯：中国直升机逼近日本护卫舰","content":"<div>\n<p>周一（3月7日）中午，在靠近东海油气田的日中中间线附近，中国国家海洋局的直升机飞近了执行监视任务的日本海上自卫队护卫舰。</p>\n<p>这架直升机在这艘日本护卫舰四周绕飞一圈，然后朝西飞去。</p>\n<p>据报道，最逼近护卫舰的距离是70米，高度仅40米。</p>\n<p>日本政府就此向中国提出抗议。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/f4zaMWQ7--bpAgXjf9Jj2M7u0KE/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/f4zaMWQ7--bpAgXjf9Jj2M7u0KE/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/f4zaMWQ7--bpAgXjf9Jj2M7u0KE/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/f4zaMWQ7--bpAgXjf9Jj2M7u0KE/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=yPeyrgC5avE:lcNrpIfv9cI:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=yPeyrgC5avE:lcNrpIfv9cI:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=yPeyrgC5avE:lcNrpIfv9cI:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=yPeyrgC5avE:lcNrpIfv9cI:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=yPeyrgC5avE:lcNrpIfv9cI:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=yPeyrgC5avE:lcNrpIfv9cI:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/yPeyrgC5avE\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):caonimaaiziyouATgmail.com</b></p>\n","author":176,"c